<section class="care-guide text-center py-5">
    <h2>Pet Care Guide</h2>
    <p>Welcome to the Pet Care Guide! Here you'll find essential tips and advice on how to care for your pets and ensure their well-being.</p>
    <ul class="care-list" style="text-align:left; max-width:600px; margin:auto;">
        <li><strong>Nutrition:</strong> Provide a balanced diet suitable for your pet's age, size, and species.</li>
        <li><strong>Exercise:</strong> Ensure regular physical activity to keep your pet healthy and happy.</li>
        <li><strong>Veterinary Care:</strong> Schedule regular check-ups and vaccinations with your vet.</li>
        <li><strong>Grooming:</strong> Maintain proper hygiene by bathing, brushing, and nail trimming as needed.</li>
        <li><strong>Safe Environment:</strong> Create a safe, comfortable, and stimulating living space for your pet.</li>
        <li><strong>Love & Attention:</strong> Spend quality time and build a strong bond with your pet.</li>
    </ul>
</section> 